    "description": "介绍由Risky Lab推出的<strong>Warbits+</strong>专利技术。启动模拟战场，以更文明的方式对抗敌人。与你的盟友不一致？没有关系！放下那些爆能枪，玩Warbits+，虚拟地粉碎对手！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/5eecf7ba13802ad1bd78c0de073e3205.poster.avif?t=1771508129\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/5eecf7ba13802ad1bd78c0de073e3205.webm?t=1771508129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/5eecf7ba13802ad1bd78c0de073e3205.mp4?t=1771508129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>战役</strong>——在5个独特的环境中进行20个任务，解开一个功能失调的星系和旨在拯救它的战争模拟器的故事。<br></li><li><strong>挑战模式</strong>——以自己的节奏挑战30个充满挑战性的任务。10个小冲突，10个智力拼图和10个可解锁的老手任务。<br></li><li><strong>地图编辑器</strong>——与社区建立、共享和玩自定义地图。<br></li><li><strong>本地和在线</strong>——与人工智能和本地玩家对战，或将战斗带到互联网的前线。<br></li><li><strong>跨平台</strong>——支持Windows、macOS、iOS和Android。<br></li><li><strong>标签匹配中心</strong>——自动匹配与你喜欢相同游戏模式的玩家，并在每月积分榜上竞争荣誉。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/15c3a4648d565b1ab43f1e6e7777eb7c.avif?t=1771508129\" width=616 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>地图编辑器</strong></h2>使用内置的地图编辑器将你的创意带到生活中。本地玩或发布到社区分享。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>标签匹配中心</strong></h2>通过参加具有自定义规则和地图轮换的独特模式，与其他玩家在线对抗。为榜首而战，观看社区回放，并渴望成为今天的胜者！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/54181915157740ddd552569f4912084f.avif?t=1771508129\" width=616 height=334 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/328c829616862f0f88d4da21153b1c49.poster.avif?t=1771508129\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/328c829616862f0f88d4da21153b1c49.webm?t=1771508129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338990/extras/328c829616862f0f88d4da21153b1c49.mp4?t=1771508129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
